msgid ":ref:`mt-modernmt` better supports language variants."
msgstr ":ref:`mt-modernmt` 에서 언어 변형을 더 잘 지원합니다."

#: changes.rst:452
msgid ""
"Automatically translated strings are now identified by a dedicated flag "
