msgstr ":ref:`hooks` 개선."

#: changes.rst:598
msgid "Now follows :ref:`api-errors`."
msgstr "이제 :ref:`api-errors` 를 따릅니다."

#: changes.rst:599
msgid "Available in the OpenAPI."
msgstr "OpenAPI에서 사용 가능."

#: changes.rst:600
