msgid "Create a Python environment:"
msgstr "Python 환경 생성:"

#: contributing/start.rst:37
msgid ""
"Install Weblate (for this you need some system dependencies, see :doc:`../"
"admin/install/source`) and all dependencies useful for development:"
msgstr ""
"Weblate 설치 (시스템 의존성이 필요함. :doc:`../admin/install/source` 참조) "
"및 개발에 유용한 모든 의존성:"

