msgid "Start a development server:"
msgstr "개발 서버 시작:"

#: contributing/start.rst:49
msgid ""
"Depending on your configuration, you might also want to start Celery workers:"
msgstr "구성에 따라 Celery 워커를 시작할 수도 있음:"

#: contributing/start.rst:55
msgid "To run a test (see :ref:`local-tests` for more details):"
msgstr "테스트 실행 (자세한 내용은 :ref:`local-tests` 참조):"

#: contributing/start.rst:69
msgid "Running Weblate locally in Docker"
msgstr "Docker에서 Weblate를 로컬로 실행"

